{"lemma":"شَمْلَة","slug":"شَمْلَة","root":"ش.م.ل","root_slug":"ش-م-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-م-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23046","n23047","n23048"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23046","headword_ar":"شَمْلَةٌ","root":"$ml","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garment of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kisaA='","text_ar":"كِسَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which one wraps,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inwraps, himself"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yu$otamalu bihi","text_ar":"يُشْتَمَلُ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"), (S, Mgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smaller than the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaTiyfap","text_ar":"قَطِيفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mi$omalN","text_ar":"مِشْمَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mi$omalapN","text_ar":"مِشْمَلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) the last two expl. by Lth as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kisaA='","text_ar":"كِسَا=ء"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having a sparse villous substance, with which one wraps himself, smaller than the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaTiyfap","text_ar":"قَطِيفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or the first signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kisaA='","text_ar":"كِسَا=ء"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which one wears in the manner of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_izaAr","text_ar":"اـِزَار"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waist-wrapper"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Msb:) or with the Arabs it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miy^ozar","text_ar":"مِيْزَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waist-wrapper"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of wool"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats'"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hair, which one wraps round him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mi$omalapN","text_ar":"مِشْمَلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is made of two pieces sewed together, with which a man wraps himself when he sleeps by night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA:) and this last, accord. to Meyd, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kisaA='","text_ar":"كِسَا=ء"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"comprising the steel with which one strikes fire, with the apparatus of this latter:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 628:) the pl. of the first is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$imaAlN","text_ar":"شِمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amalaAtN","text_ar":"شَمَلَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mi$omaAlN","text_ar":"مِشْمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  [Hence the saying,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dam~a Ealayohi All~ayolu $amolatahu","text_ar":"ضَمَّ عَلَيْهِ اللَّيْلُ شَمْلَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The night contracted upon him its covering of darkness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^um~u $amolapa","text_ar":"اُمُّ شَمْلَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The present world,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its enjoyments;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~unoyaA","text_ar":"الدُّنْيَا"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAar, K, TA:) so called because compassing the intellect of a man ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta$otamilu EalaY","text_ar":"تَشْتَمِلُ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaqolihi","text_ar":"عَقْلِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"), and concealing it. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wine:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, K, TA:) so called for the same reason. (TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sun."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Z, TA; and T in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Am","text_ar":"ام"},{"kind":"text","text":")."}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","K","TA","Msb","Az","IAar","AA"]},{"entry_id":"n23047","headword_ar":"شِمْلَةٌ","root":"$ml","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ai$otimaAl","text_ar":"اِشْتِمَال"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wrapping oneself with a garment"},{"kind":"text","text":"as expl. above: see 8]. (K, TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$imolapu AlS~am~aA='u","text_ar":"الشِمْلَةُ الصَّمَّا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mode of wrapping oneself"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is without a shirt and without drawers beneath;"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the case of which, prayer is disliked. (TA. [See 8, and see also art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sm","text_ar":"صم"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n23048","headword_ar":"شَمَلَةٌ","root":"$ml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amalN","text_ar":"شَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}